summary: Here is young female Redguard character. It is a clean (mostly) savegame. Sasha now lives in a hunting camp near Helgen. She has default stats and ability. To start the main quest you need a mod  \"Alternate Start - Live Another Life\".
descriptionHtml:
Here is young female Redguard character. It is a clean (mostly) savegame. Sasha now lives in a hunting camp near Helgen. She has default stats and ability.
In order to continue to play without a problem you need to install a mod:
\"Alternate Start - Live Another Life\"   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9557
As for appearance I use and recommend you the following mods:
- UNP BLESSED BODY UNPB - Now with Jiggle BBP 2.2  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899
- ApachiiSkyHair  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
- Coverwomen  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3563
- Covereyes  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4869
and all possible animations by this author: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/183089

I\'m curious to know your opinion. Please leave your comment. If you like my mod do not forget to endorse.

This savegame file created using Skyrim TESV v.1.6.89.0
author: ortog
